data.description: This beautiful home is located in Central Fort Walton Beach, one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the area. It is conveniently situated by all bases, making it the perfect choice for those who are stationed here. With a spacious and versatile floor plan, this home features a separate living area that can easily be converted into an additional bedroom or living room, providing the flexibility to adapt to any family's needs.The roof of this home was recently replaced in 2022. The water heater was installed in 2011, and the HVAC system is relatively new, at only around five years old. In addition to the impressive indoor features, this home also boasts a deep well in the backyard, providing access to fresh water for gardening or other outdoor needs. The 20 x 32 storage shed with electricity is perfect for a workshop or additional storage space, while the covered carport provides shelter for vehicles or outdoor equipment. With all of these amazing features and more, this home is a must-see for anyone looking for a comfortable and convenient lifestyle in Fort Walton Beach. Make an offer today!
